4Geeks Academy offers a "Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence," designed for professionals interested in integrating AI into their roles across various industries. No prior knowledge is needed, making it accessible to all. The course spans 6 weeks, featuring 2 live, online classes per week, with a class size limited to 12 participants. Participants will earn an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate upon completion. The program covers essential AI concepts, including generative AI, context, prompts, and models, empowering students to effectively implement AI in their workplaces. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop